{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why-- and then, of course, after [INAUDIBLE], after-- the-- residents, you know, the Jewish residents who were not citizens of Germany were, you know, were simply deported to, you know, to No Man's Land.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I remember my oldest brother went down there because my mother has a cousin who lived in Halle in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His son is still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He actually was-- he was [INAUDIBLE] Aliyah He went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wasn't home anymore when [INAUDIBLE] happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So quite a number of Jews came, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then of course, the Jewish community tried to-- the Jewish council, I mean, tried to-- tried to help along.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then we became much more aware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But still, you know, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We always were saying so foolishly-- we were saying, I remember, that our generation is the first generation that never lived through a war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I think, sometimes when we talked about it among us as friends, because there was the League of Nations, and what they did and what they didn't do for the Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- Now of course, you know much more of what was happening at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Your husband told us after the fact that you-- that you were sort of secretly engaged, or you were boyfriend and girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did you come to meet your husband?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we [? met ?] we met in Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, because it wasn't even secretly engaged.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was we were going to get married after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he might have not been very acceptable to my parents, either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, I say-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We met-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Lodz, you know, became part of-- of the German Reich.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
